WEBVTT

00:02.500 --> 00:05.100
The photos link 
Ray Fiske to Gregory Malina.

00:05.100 --> 00:07.400
Patty used it as leverage 
against Fiske.

00:07.700 --> 00:08.900
Do you regret what we did?

00:08.900 --> 00:09.800
Because I do.

00:10.600 --> 00:12.200
I did everything you asked me to.

00:12.300 --> 00:13.700
You said I'd be taken care of.

00:13.800 --> 00:17.200
Mr. Popler is leaking 
information to Frobisher's camp.

00:17.300 --> 00:18.200
Ellen, it's me.

00:18.500 --> 00:21.400
Katie brought you a videotape 
that Gregory Malina made.

00:21.500 --> 00:24.600
Do anything you have to do, 
but get me that tape.

00:25.500 --> 00:27.100
We went to Patty Hewes'apartment.

00:27.100 --> 00:28.200
We didn't find the tape.

00:28.300 --> 00:29.800
No matter what you think,

00:29.900 --> 00:33.300
- I didn't have anything to 
do with any of this.
- I know.

00:33.600 --> 00:35.900
I've been accused of murder, 
and you're going to exonerate me.

00:35.900 --> 00:37.100
Then I'll give you the tape.

00:37.200 --> 00:38.900
Ellen Parsons is out on bail.

00:39.100 --> 00:40.300
You know where to find her.

